title: Delegation of Authority Under Section 208(d)(6) of the Compact of Free Association Amendments Act of 2024
summary: This Presidential Memorandum, dated November 20, 2025, delegates the President's authority to submit a report to Congress, as required by section 208(d)(6) of the Compact of Free Association Amendments Act of 2024, to the Secretary of State. The Secretary of State is directed to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.
